        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-num">18</div><div><div class="faq-q">How does Construction-to-Perm work for senior DPMs?</div><div class="faq-a">Construction-to-Perm Single-Close funds FL construction (12-18 months) then converts to permanent without re-qualifying. Senior DPMs building custom Florida primary residence (Tampa Bay, Naples, Coral Gables, Jacksonville waterfront concentration).</div></div></div>
