        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-num">23</div><div><div class="faq-q">Are there FL-specific considerations for DPMs?</div><div class="faq-a">FL no state income tax preserves substantial income. FL retirement population substantial diabetic foot + wound care + reconstructive surgery demand. FL hospital system expansion (HCA, AdventHealth, BayCare, Memorial) substantial DPM employment opportunity. Barry University Florida DPM training pipeline.</div></div></div>
